Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Sprinkle both sides of steak with seasoned salt. Place in a foil-lined baking dish with 3 tablespoons of water. Pour salsa over steak, and spread chopped vegetables all around pan. Cover, and seal with foil. Bake in the preheated oven for one hour, or to desired doneness. Serve immediately.